22:56.242 --> 22:57.844
Cattie Goodman
fixed Smoot!

22:57.877 --> 22:59.846
Yes, you did,
Cattie Goodman.

22:59.879 --> 23:02.348
So I-I guess you're
probably gonna look

23:02.381 --> 23:04.350
for a new school
to fix, huh?

23:04.383 --> 23:05.785
Oh, good idea, Tam-Tam.

23:05.818 --> 23:08.020
Get me another feather
in my cap.

23:08.054 --> 23:09.188
Call the district,

23:09.221 --> 23:11.524
tell them that Quinn's ready
to take the reins.

23:11.558 --> 23:12.925
Whatever it takes to make it

23:12.959 --> 23:15.862
so I don't have to come back
to this unholy lake of fire!

23:15.895 --> 23:19.231
Now, where are
my write-up forms?!

23:19.265 --> 23:22.935
Because I swear to God,
when I finally find them,

23:22.969 --> 23:24.403
you will die!

23:24.437 --> 23:26.205
[ Whispering ]
Now, be honest with me --

23:26.238 --> 23:27.774
Brock's best friend,
Hawk Remington...

23:27.807 --> 23:28.708
Oh, God.

23:28.741 --> 23:30.209
...is that me?

23:30.242 --> 23:31.377
Probably.
Probably, sure.

23:31.410 --> 23:33.245
[ Chuckles ]
I knew it was me!

23:33.279 --> 23:36.483
And that scene where you and I
tandem paraglide

23:36.516 --> 23:39.385
over that topless beach -- that
is just classic Quinn and Loren.

23:39.418 --> 23:41.588
Quinn, we've never done that
before.

23:41.621 --> 23:43.122
You take care
of yourself, okay?

23:43.155 --> 23:44.423
Thank you, Tammy.
I will.

23:44.457 --> 23:48.060
I swear to God, I am punishing
you so good right now...

23:48.094 --> 23:51.397
because you will never,
ever do this again!

23:51.430 --> 23:53.132
-Tammy, one more thing.
-Yes?

23:53.165 --> 23:56.068
Tam, the third-floor women's
[bleep] is clogged again.

23:56.102 --> 23:57.937
-Mm-hmm.
-And I think it was Julie.

23:57.970 --> 24:00.973
[ Laughs ]
Julie did it.

24:01.007 --> 24:03.510
Ooh.
Crazy-ass bitch.

24:03.543 --> 24:05.912
Now, when can we expect
a sequel?

24:05.945 --> 24:07.079
I am outlining.

24:07.113 --> 24:08.347
Quinn told me
to come in here,

24:08.380 --> 24:10.282
but did I just see Cattie
drive across the lawn?

24:10.316 --> 24:13.119
Sounds about right.
Quinn's back in charge now.

24:13.152 --> 24:17.323
And that's why you're gonna have
to live in my house with me

24:17.356 --> 24:20.459
to have a positive
male role model!

24:20.493 --> 24:21.794
He sounds angry.

24:21.828 --> 24:24.263
Oh, it's all for show.
He's in there, tickling Loren.

24:24.296 --> 24:25.297
-[ Laughs ]
-Right there.

24:25.331 --> 24:26.365
That's it, right there.

24:26.398 --> 24:28.300
Why don't you go
on home?

24:28.334 --> 24:30.136
I'll get you
off the hook.

24:30.169 --> 24:31.137
Thank you.

24:31.170 --> 24:33.405
[ Sighs ]

24:33.840 --> 24:35.474
[ Sign clatters ]
